{"type": "article", "id": 2483, "title": "Moleskine 创意笔记本", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-22T08:39:34Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232503KxqlPcDouN3t8dw1.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t作为世界上最受追捧的笔记本品牌之一，Moleskine 日前携手包括 Rodrigo Almeida 、BCXSY、Tord Boontje、Antonio Marras 在内的多位设计师，带来了一项名为“ hacked by design ”的创意笔记本展，总计有超过 250 本笔记本亮相，除了可以在<a href=\"http://www.londondesignfestival.com/\" target=\"_blank\">伦敦设计节</a>上欣赏到这些作品之外，它们还将亮相于伦敦的 Moleskine 各门店。事实上，这些笔记本早在 2006年就开始在包括巴黎、纽约、东京等地巡回展览。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232501RQ5G2AlEtPhYJoNz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.575\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232501o2Cl9Ebm8YBPnJhI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7921875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232502s3YFlrX4oIgyQ7MC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7453125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232502tKS7vuMafbIHDsXj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6265625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232503ptkmLC43hsg5J7rH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}